# Secrets / credentials (never commit)
# Scoped to credential *data* files — broad prefixes like "credentials*" are
# avoided so they cannot silently shadow source modules (e.g. credentials.py).
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
.credentials
.secrets
credentials*.json
credentials*.yaml
credentials*.yml
secrets*.json
secrets*.yaml
secrets*.yml

